Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs33\pos(949,664)}Page One
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也曾經憑運氣一口氣衝入始頁十二人
